</style><p>布斯波！即使在2023年4月28日平均订阅人数上升至日本第二位后，由于新艺人的稳定出道以及附属艺人的订阅人数的稳定增长，平均订阅人数仍在继续增加。可以看出，就频道订户数量而言，他们正在巩固日本第二的地位。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="kfJcGXM2vD"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-vspo-has-risen-to-2nd-place-in-japan-in-terms-of-average-number-of-youtube-subscribers-among-affiliated-17-talents/">VTuber团体Buspo！ 17名附属艺人的平均订阅数位居日本第2位</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber 团体 Buspo! 17 名附属艺人的平均订阅人数在日本排名第二” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-vspo-has-risen-to-2nd-place-in-japan-in-terms-of-average-number-of-youtube-subscribers-among-affiliated-17-talents/embed/#?secret=NVqZRi3esv#?secret=kfJcGXM2vD" data-secret="kfJcGXM2vD" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="IH6kLN0SvH"><a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-aizawa-ema-reached-500k-youtube-subscribers-the-6th-talent-on-vspo/">相泽艾玛 (Emma Aizawa) 订阅人数突破 50 万 Buspop!第六位VTuber</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“艾玛·相泽订阅人数突破 50 万，Buspo！第六位 VTuber” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-aizawa-ema-reached-500k-youtube-subscribers-the-6th-talent-on-vspo/embed/#?secret=lplEU2n1sh#?secret=IH6kLN0SvH" data-secret="IH6kLN0SvH" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="o1QVREIZP1"><a href="https://p2y.jp/vspo-new